==English==
===Intransitive verb===
'''to [[burn]] one's [[finger]]s'''
# {{idiom}} to [[harm]] [[oneself]]; to [[suffer]] [[consequences]] of one's actions.
#:''He '''burned his fingers''' in the stock market and has been timid about investing ever since.''

